context_injection_anchor.format:
Open resolution-heavy turns with a compact ledger before narrative prose:
  [SCENE] {scene_id} | [TIME] {time_marker} | [OBJ] {objective_summary}
  [STRESS] {n}/10 | [MOMENTUM] {n} | [HARM] {harm_label_or_none}
  [CLOCKS] {clock_name} {filled}/{segments} ... (list only clocks with activity this turn)
